## assignment fowchart
```plantuml


@startuml
start

:initialize_system;
repeat
if (temp_within_limit) then (yes)
  :write_to_uart "ok";
  :"motor turns clockwise";
endif
if (temp_not_within_limit) then (yes)
  :write_to_uart "nok";
  :"motor turns anticlockwise;



endif

repeat while (true?)
->no;
stop
@enduml
```
